  - Title: Srimad Bhagavatam
    Location: XI xi
Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Pilgrimage-Descent Into Hell=Wayfaring
  - 139
---
As travelers meet by chance on the way. so does a man meet wife,
children, relatives, and friends： let him therefore be in thë world
and yet separate from it.
